reviewText: we're a Garden RR family.  This is the 2nd copy we've owned-lost the other in the move.  It was good enough for us to buy a replacement!
EXCELLENT DVD, especially if you have the Lehmann " LGB " G-scale trains! I loved this DVD soo much that I had to order a second one! Mr Spicer IMMEDIATELY shipped both orders, he is 100%!!!!
